{"tid":428093,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"沒有iPhone的日子第一日","createTime":"2017-10-07T19:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T20:32:45.000Z","uid":146014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"91132f84fc9f73e84e994558af4e099b9d29ad1f","tid":428093,"uid":146014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T19:55:13.000Z","msg":"話說尋晩部iPhone用用下無啦啦自動熄機<br />\n從此就開唔到機了<br />\n點差電 點㩒掣都無反應 收咗皮<br />\n突然發現:<br />\n帶表好重要 因為無得睇時間<br />\n認路好重要 因為無得睇Google Map<br />\n準時好重要 因為無得係wtsapp group say sorry會遲<br />\n<br />\n其實自己真係唔係呢個年代嘅人<br />\n中學到依家都重用緊mp3聽歌<br />\n其實無電話姐 <br />\n返到屋企又可以開電腦look fb ig<br />\n無wtsapp但重有telegram FBmessenger<br />\n<br />\n搭地鐵 係餐廳食野 好專心觀察下人<br />\n有d慶幸自己終於唔再係低頭族<br />\n<br />\n突然係到諗自己老豆老母以前long D點keep<br />\n無skype好少用電話 明信片要寄十世 (利申老豆行船)<br />\n<br />\n維修中心話要14日工作天<br />\n其實隔下世清靜下都好<br />\n歡迎lm睇我忍到幾耐"},{"pid":"fd9ec3c267aed2fcae215729d7f80b7eb0f6bab7","tid":428093,"uid":86378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T19:58:21.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都試過有一個禮拜冇電話用，係好唔方便，但真係發現咗好多之前自己冇留意嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2ded2208e797a8d1f21caaf8aa07bc0553d02b","tid":428093,"uid":146014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T20:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/040216_c7fdb2ea687ae4adb5954df76ffce2c7.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F040216_c7fdb2ea687ae4adb5954df76ffce2c7.JPG&h=c1573b45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/040216_0e83bb8b45e8907a653b905cb269f203.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F040216_0e83bb8b45e8907a653b905cb269f203.JPG&h=5b0a4294&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de0ba2640eebdceca4726f72caf82114fc2998df","tid":428093,"uid":33749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T20:32:45.000Z","msg":"三年前試過玩極限深潛一個禮拜<br />\n連到上網嘅嘢都唔開<br />\n<br />\n其實搵到第二啲嘢做就唔會話需要忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰排我行山游水飲茶睇電視睇報紙睇返細個啲舊相舊嘢<br />\n都唔覺得要忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係班friend有嘢玩先上返水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋最接受唔到係行山時見到靚景冇得影低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}